* to achieve something similar to the example from the comments, the code below creates &lt;s&gt;1440&lt;/s&gt; 1441 possible labels for the yAxis (for each possible minute). The getHourString() function converts minutes to labels (e.g. `121` becomes `02:01`)
```js
