Below I provide a method which can demonstrates one way this particular task can be accomplished. In this example, you provide a comma (,) delimited **Words String** (just like you already do with your code example) and you also provide a Puzzle String. The method will return a List&lt;String&gt; collection where each element of that list will contain:

 - A line containing the actual shuffled Puzzle String;
